room_title: Escape room "S3R1AL" by Exit Plan in Washington, D.C.
room_address: 201 Royal SE Suite F Leesburg, VA 20175
room_description:
You awaken to darkness, and realize you are trapped…a captive in a room you cannot see.  You scream, but no one can hear you. Or can they? You hear something move. There is someone in there with you.
Is it HIM? No, thankfully HE is gone… but HE WILL be back. And you have 60 short minutes to free yourself and your fellow captives from his twisted lair. Join several other victims and try to break free from the deranged serial killer.
